      • generateFilteredReport

        public static void generateFilteredReport​(User user,
                                          Integer minAge,
                                          Integer maxAge,
                                          MaritalStatus maritalStatus,
                                          String projectName,
                                          FlatType flatType)
        Generate a report for booked applications with filters. Setting the respective filter values to null will ignore the filter.
        Parameters:
        user - The HDB Manager generating the report.
        minAge - The minimum age of applicants.
        maxAge - The maximum age of applicants.
        maritalStatus - The marital status of applicants.
        projectName - The name of the project.
        flatType - The type of flat booked.
